##### **Intuition :-**
* Take a variable `prev` and point it with element at 0th index of `vector nums`.
* Take a variable count and initialize it with 1 as we are already escaping the 0th index.
* Take a variable pos in which we will insert any new element which is not equal to prev and update prev with new and increment the pos and count at same time.
